Ring nuclease browser for Type III CRISPR-Cas

This website is released as Supplementary Material for a manuscript in preparation. Currently for review only.

Instructions
  • Add filters by clicking "Add Condition".
  • Hover your mouse over the figures to enlarge them.
  • Columns and rows can be reordered.
  • Download the (filtered) data by clicking Export to Excel.
  • Note that the table scrolls horizontally.
Locus visualisations
  • Red: NCBI annotations
  • Green: CCTyper annotations
  • Blue: Our effector annotations
  • Yellow: Our ring nuclease annotations
  • Grey: CRISPR-Cas locus boundary
